Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:03.20,Yellow,,0,0,0,,(off) "Trobar algú especial és un enigma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:07.04,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Però els enigmes d'un cas són encara més apassionants.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:10.52,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"L'escenari d'avui és un edifici normal i corrent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:13.24,Yellow,,0,0,0,,"Tindré una colla d'actors al voltant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:16.88,Yellow,,0,0,0,,Té el cervell d'un adult i és... el detectiu Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:22.68,Songs,,0,0,0,,Unmei no ruuretto mawashite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:30.52,Songs,,0,0,0,,zutto kimi wo mite ita!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:40.16,Songs,,0,0,0,,Naze na no konna ni shiawase na no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:47.04,Songs,,0,0,0,,Suiheisen wo miru to kanashiku naru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:59.72,Songs,,0,0,0,,Ano koro no jibun wo tooku de mite iru sonna kanji!
